  <h4>A little bit about me.</h4>
  <p>My name is Gabriel Muñumel. I'm an enthusiastic and proactive web and app
    developer. I'm specialized in web frameworks such as:
    <%= link_to 'Ruby on Rails', url_for('http://rubyonrails.org/') %>,
    <%= link_to 'Django', url_for('https://www.djangoproject.com/') %>,
    <%= link_to 'Symfony', url_for('http://symfony.com/') %> and
    <%= link_to 'CodeIgniter', url_for('http://www.codeigniter.com/') %>.
    I've developed systems from a simple static web page to a complex e-commerce.
    In <%= link_to 'Android', url_for('https://www.android.com/') %> ecosystem,
    I've develop applications to streaming radio music and share likes.</p>
  <div class="spacer"></div>
  <h4>I make software of quality!</h4>
  <p>I've develop many websites over the years: from a simple static website to
    a complex e-commerce. I like to work with web frameworks because they give you
    a solid ground to build your system based on using the best practices, patterns
    and they're supported by a big community of developers. </p>
  <p>My systems are characterized by being simple to use, easy to navigate, robust
    and scalable. I also pay a lot attention in the testing aspect to build quality
    software. </p>
  <div class="spacer"></div>
  <h4>And I offer packages for you!</h4>
  <p>I can offer three packages to develop your system. They go from a simple
    package: static website, passing through a system working with a database and
    managing large amount of information to an e-commerce (similar to Amazon or eBay).
    These packages are flexible and they can adapt to the client's needs.</p>
